            <div class="li">
                <li>Origin</li>
                <p>Origin is a git shorthand name for a remote repository that a project was cloned from. Origin uses the name of the cloned repo due to origin acting as a alias on the users system. Origin is used when we want to push changes to the original repo.</p>
